d. The Company shall also be entitled to terminate with immediate effect, in the event of a just
cause including misconduct by you such as
(a) consistent non-performance of your duties/services;
(b) disciplinary action;
(c) causing damage to Company's property including without limitation to
data in or under the control of the Company;
(d) excessive uninformed absenteeism for more than 5 days and tardiness in relation to the hours of work;
(e) In case of such termination due reasons listed above, you shall not be entitled to receive
Compensation or any statutory payments in lieu of notice period to be served;
(f) If you cease your employment without serving notice period or if the notice period is not
served completely, the Company may withhold the relieving letter and the other documents,
may recover the equivalent amount to the salary amount that you would have accrued during
the notice period from you in lieu of the notice period, or even take legal action against you;
(g) violation of any intellectual property rights, non-compete and non-disclosure of confidential
information provisions, undertaking or any of the terms, conditions, policies and guidelines as
enumerated in this letter, Confidentiality and IP Assignment Agreement and/or in its policies,
and/or any other conditions specifically provided to you relating to your service with Company;
(h) wilful omission, negligent acts, suppression of facts, misrepresentation, any acts of fraud
or forgery made by you including but not limited to any criminal proceedings instituted or any
other legal actions (whatsoever in nature) enforced against you by any judicial and/or quasi-bodies,
enforcement and/or governmental/regulatory/statutory authorities;

